# Full Owner CMS ‚Äî Architecture & Reference

This file works alongside `admin-panel-audit.mdc` (admin panel bugs & API) and `deploy-commands.mdc` (quick reference). Together they give any developer full context on the codebase.

## How It Works

```
Owner edits in Admin ‚Üí Settings ‚Üí Website Settings
  ‚Üí PUT /api/site-settings          (bulk key/value save)
  ‚Üí POST /api/site-settings/upload  (image upload)
    ‚Üí site_settings DB table (key/value rows)
    ‚Üí Laravel Cache (auto-busted on every save via SiteSetting::bust())
      ‚Üí Blade views read SiteSetting::get('key', 'fallback')
        ‚Üí Public website updates instantly
```

